{
  "stem": "4276.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when my brother came back after maybe few weeks, the Gestapo came in our house-- first in the store because we had lots of equipment that people could listen out of the country even, with the radio equipment.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they looked for my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And because the father couldn't be found because he was away, then they took my brother who was only 15 years old.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was the man.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember he-- they went to our house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were very close between the store, with the business and house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they asked my mother to stay in the business, and I was that time there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they say, don't go with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then when they left, the maid was called our store that we should come right away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They beat my brother very badly, and, and they left him with-- you know, I never thought about those things till now.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was supposed to go with my mother the next day to Gestapo and bring-- he had a little gun it was-- yeah, it was a gun that he was playing like all the young people would play.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he beat him with that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this was very painful because when his-- my mother came in and saw this swelling and all this-- well, it was very sad.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then my mother was so sorry that we didn't run away at that night before she went to Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they took him to this prison first for a few, few weeks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I think two weeks he was there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were still in Cracow, not in ghetto, so it must have been-- and they took him in May or June-- this I don't remember-- and to this prison.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
